text: Veynes is a commune in the Hautes-Alpes department. == Population == == Transport == === Road === The D20, D48, D320, D348, D648, D937E, D994 and D994B roads pass through the commune. === Rail === Veynes has a train station called Gare de Veynes. == References == Category:Communes in Hautes-Alpes
title: Veynes
